graph LR
    subgraph Walker ["Walker threads (2-4)"]
        W1["walker 1"]
        W2["walker 2"]
        W3["walker ..."]
    end

    subgraph Searcher ["Search threads (N CPUs)"]
        S1["searcher 1"]
        S2["searcher 2"]
        S3["searcher ..."]
    end

    DirQueue["directory queue"] --> W1 & W2 & W3
    W1 & W2 & W3 -->|PathBuf| FileChannel["file channel"]
    FileChannel --> S1 & S2 & S3
    S1 & S2 & S3 -->|Mutex| Stdout["stdout BufWriter"]
